Dlala Thukzin:
Dlala Thukzin have 5 songs on the Spotify Top 200 Weekly South Africa chart. 
 They first appeared on the chart on 2021-07-29. Their most recent appearance has been on 2024-01-18. They have a total of 13412955 million streams. 
. His highest position on the chart is 1 for the song iPlan which was at this position on 2023-10-12
 The songs of his that have appeared on the chart are Danki Bawo ... Imoto ... Phuze ... Phuze (Remix) (Radio Edit) ... iPlan
